title: VA (Jazzy) Funk - The Good Times (Dutch Treat ^C063 HQ)
description:
Sometime ago I was looking for some good Funk tracks. But every Funk lover knows that the recordings are quite bad and so its not played much often. Pity, so its now time for funk. I had already a small list (Wanna Funk) but it took a bit longer before I had enough tracks to fill a whole and well balanced 2,6-hour playlist..... Enjoy,

PS: And again the software does not work. So sorry no wonderful cover.
